                            <p>At South Island, well-being is at the heart of everything that we do. We want our school to be healthy, inclusive and supportive so that it enables our community to thrive. We promote positive mental health and well-being for our whole school community and recognise how important it is in our lives.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_wellbeing/">
