                        <img src="/cache/img/4c02f6375e48f7dd7948619324ca86fc.jpg" alt="family support structure" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>FAMILY SUPPORT STRUCTURE</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>The SIS Family Leadership Team provides pastoral support to help all students flourish. Each student has trusted adults, including Tutors, Heads of Year, Counsellors, and Medical Professionals, ensuring holistic support.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_wellbeing/">
