                            <h3>
                                <span>TUTORS</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>The role of the Tutor is a crucial one as they are advocates for their students and they serve as the main adult point of contact, gathering information from other teachers about what the student needs and spearheading efforts to support them. Tutors make every effort to ensure that the relationships fostered between the student, home and school are positive.</p>
