        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            const ori_total = parseInt($('#section4').data('total'));
            let slider_loop = ori_total >= 3 ? true : false;
            $('#section4').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: slider_loop,
                dummySlide: slider_loop,
				afterSlide: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
					if(slider_loop) {
						if(current_page == ori_total) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2).Slider('start');
						}
						if(current_page == ori_total * 2 + 1) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total + 1).Slider('start');
						}
					}
				},
                afterInit: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
                    if(slider_loop) {
                        slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2);
                    }
                    else {
                        slider.Slider('jump', total_page);
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section5" data-total="6">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bg bg-colour3"></div>
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Values in Action</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="record-slider">
            <div class="slider-container">
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/12177bd9c3aee57015be6d7fe7a85aef.jpg" alt="sports" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>SPORTS</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>South Island promotes physical activity with a wide range of sports and impressive facilities. Students achieve success, representing their school and Hong Kong SAR, fostering involvement, activity, and competitiveness at all levels.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/19980db227f4f813138ec40412db27c7.jpg" alt="activities" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>ACTIVITIES</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>South Island offers diverse extracurricular activities, fostering skill development, personal growth, and relationships with dedicated teachers and coaches in a well-structured program that extends the curriculum and pushes students beyond their comfort zone.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/7276cfdd2025a207ef4789e188adf57a.jpg" alt="interhouse" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>INTERHOUSE</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>The House system at South Island consists of 6 Houses. Through our various Interhouse activities, students are given chances to develop supportive vertical relationships with students across all year levels, establish strong school spirit, and provide a sense of belonging and ownership for each student.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/our_houses/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/8be0367f79441af3f39c7ae4848501e2.jpg" alt="STUDENT LEADERSHIP" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>STUDENT LEADERSHIP</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>South Island School offers over X student-led councils, initiatives and special events.  Through these student-led activities, SIS students are empowered to live out the school motto, develop important soft skills as student leaders, and make a difference in the various areas that they are passionate about.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/student_leadership/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/3db80986e0cb6a4f421645f097d88372.jpg" alt="community" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>COMMUNITY ENGAGEMENT</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>All students will have the opportunity to engage and participate in the community as part of their required coursework at South Island School.  Students will learn to engage in our local community and cultivate a service mindset as they make a difference in Hong Kong and beyond.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/community_service/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/490517998341d909a69629e4f93d879a.jpg" alt="Mad Week" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>MAD WEEK!</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>Each year at South Island School, we dedicate a week to our motto “Making a Difference.” Students engage in diverse local and international activities focused on Creativity, Activity, and Service.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/12177bd9c3aee57015be6d7fe7a85aef.jpg" alt="sports" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>SPORTS</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>South Island promotes physical activity with a wide range of sports and impressive facilities. Students achieve success, representing their school and Hong Kong SAR, fostering involvement, activity, and competitiveness at all levels.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/19980db227f4f813138ec40412db27c7.jpg" alt="activities" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>ACTIVITIES</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>South Island offers diverse extracurricular activities, fostering skill development, personal growth, and relationships with dedicated teachers and coaches in a well-structured program that extends the curriculum and pushes students beyond their comfort zone.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/school_activities/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/7276cfdd2025a207ef4789e188adf57a.jpg" alt="interhouse" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>INTERHOUSE</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>The House system at South Island consists of 6 Houses. Through our various Interhouse activities, students are given chances to develop supportive vertical relationships with students across all year levels, establish strong school spirit, and provide a sense of belonging and ownership for each student.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://sis.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/our_houses/">
