            <div class="lightbox" data-id="153">
            <div class="lightbox-wrapper">
                <button class="close"></button>
                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>10/02/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>Galloping into the Year of the Horse! 🐎✨<br><br> Today’s Chinese New Year Assembly was nothing short of spectacular. From the grace of traditional dances to the powerful resonance of traditional instruments, our performers truly brought the spirit of the zodiac to life. We are feeling inspired, energized, and ready for a year of growth!</h3>
